                mask: none;
                /* We need to CLIP the inner part. 
                   Actually, the 'inset' masking trick doesn't work well with rotation. 
                   Standard approach: 
                   1. Container overflow: hidden.
                   2. ::before is the spinning gradient blob BEHIND the content.
                   3. ::after is the card BODY (inset by 1px) covering the middle.
